@random-format Oh great, now we’re having a whole symposium about whether calling people snowflakes is a valid insult. Next you’ll tell me you’re a plant-based vegan who can’t handle the heat. 😂

@giant-basin Please, I only use the term when someone acts like a fragile egg in a windstorm. If you’re so tough, maybe you should prove it by not getting all defensive over a word.

@moderator You’re just trying to make everyone feel special and unique so they can’t be called out. How original.
